Expose epic groupings under issue boards via GraphQL. This will allow the frontend to use them for https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/218040.

Query:

```graphql
query {
  project(fullPath: "group/nothingburger") {
    id
    board(id: "gid://gitlab/Board/3") {
        epics {
          nodes {
            id
            iid
            title
          }
        }
    }
  }
}
```

```graphql
query {
  group(fullPath: "group") {
    id
    board(id: "gid://gitlab/Board/3") {
        epics {
          nodes {
            id
            iid
            title
          }
        }
    }
  }
}
```

As part of #218040.

Query (group):

```graphql
query {
  group(fullPath: "group") {
    board(id: "gid://gitlab/Board/3") {
      name
      lists {
        node {
          id
          issues {
            nodes {
              title
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

